page_title: Azure OpenAI Service encryption of data at rest
page_description: Learn how Azure OpenAI encrypts your data when it's persisted to the cloud.
chunk_content: Use a different keyTo change the key that you use for encryption, follow these steps:1. Go to your Azure AI services resource, and then select Encryption.1. Enter the URI for the new key. Alternately, you can select the key vault and then select a new key.1. Save your changes.
